item.description:
@black_birds0 wrote:

[quote=“chri55w, post:14, topic:377569”]Hi,
me and a friend are currently also looking at setting up an Rsps however we are having issues with coding, and cannot find a coder, we are both very experienced, have been playing runescape for around 4 years on and off and private servers for many months now, we have a lot of ideas for improvements, i also have connections with an extremely talented web designer whom i have discussed the possibility of setting up a website for an rsps, he has agreed to do so and will be able to set up a website including internal forums, and other features for a decent price,

your server is impressive and looks strong however there are a few features which could effect the economy such as the already mentioned ::cash command for donators and if you sell the moderator rights you would have issues with abusers, i have many more suggestions, and would like to discuss them more but privatleyi am able to put a lot of time into this server and its community, i would be able to help the members of the community, help you go through donations and much more, i hope you consider this as a serious proposal and i hope to talk to you further about it if you wish to contact me externally then please contact one of the following:

Email/msn:Chri5walters@msn.com
skype:chri55w
Alrite u got a deal
thanks for your time

chris[/quote]
